places.address: drgaa msiidi, Sadalga Dargha, Sadalga, Sadalaga Rural, Karnataka 591239

featured_reviews.review_id: Alhamdulillah. Tanggal 16 Januari 2019, sampai di Sadalga dalam rangka silaturahmi dengan orang-orang muslim di wilayah ini. Di samping masjid ada kuburan wali Allah namanya Khwaja Shamnamira Dargah Sadalga, yang selalu ramai diziarahi. Jika kami mencuci pakaian, menjemurnya mesti di atap masjid, pemandangan yang indah. Dan ada kejutan lain, disini ternyata banyak sekali monyet, suatu kali jemuran kami berantakan diobrak-abrik monyet. Saudara-saudara disini sangat baik dan ramah-ramah, kami sering dibawa berkunjung kerumah-rumah warga muslim wilayah ini. Semoga semua kebaikan mereka dibalas Allah dengan surga. Amiin..

featured_reviews.review_translated_text: Alhamdulillah. January 16 2019, arrived at Sadalga in the framework of friendship with Muslims in this region. Next to the mosque is the grave of a saint named Khwaja Shamnamira Dargah Sadalga, who is always crowded with pilgrimages. If we wash clothes, we have to dry them on the roof of the mosque, a beautiful sight. And there was another surprise, there were lots of monkeys here, one time our clothesline was torn apart by monkeys. The brothers and sisters here are very kind and friendly, we are often taken to visit the homes of Muslim residents in this area. May all their kindness be rewarded by Allah with heaven. Amen..
